attr.title: Sunset Witch Classic
attr.desc: Sunset Witch is traveling over the ocean when an army of Bob fish attack. The more she takes down the faster things get, and it's up to her to bring peace to the ocean's surface!
attr.inst: Download the game from https://angusbeer.itch.io/sunset-witch-classic and add the exe file to the sunsetwitchclassic/gamedata folder.
